      ],
      "updated": 1770405116530,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "wsgi -> 4 worker\nhow to decide worker\ncore\nRAM size\nin wsgi if one request gone it whole should be complete for other request to run on that worker\n\n\nasync await -> code control\nconcurrency -> prepmptive tasking -> Os control\n\ndjango -> wsgi -> gunicorn -> 8 worker -> inside worker 1 request  -> if we have a task that is independent we can run in celery\nfastapi -> awsgi -> gunicorn -> 8 worker -> inside worker uvicorn multiple request due to async await\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "wsgi -> 4 worker\nhow to decide worker\ncore\nRAM size\nin wsgi if one request gone it whole should be complete for other request to run on that worker\n\n\nasync await -> code control\nconcurrency -> prepmptive tasking -> Os control\n\ndjango -> wsgi -> gunicorn -> 8 worker -> inside worker 1 request  -> if we have a task that is independent we can run in celery\nfastapi -> awsgi -> gunicorn -> 8 worker -> inside worker uvicorn multiple request due to async await\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
